Name: kata
Description: Alias of the default runtime handler (usually the same as kata-qemu)

Name: kata-qemu-coco-dev
Description: CoCo without an enclave (for testing only)

Name: kata-qemu-sev
Description: CoCo with QEMU for AMD SEV HW

Name: kata-qemu-snp
Description: CoCo with QEMU for AMD SNP HW

Name: kata-qemu-tdx
Description: CoCo with QEMU for Intel TDX HW

Name: kata-qemu-se
Description: CoCO with QEMU for Secure Execution

Name: enclave-cc
Description: CoCo with enclave-cc (process-based isolation without Kata)
